OL,3,CConcern over children's welfare in
OL,4,Csport sees contacts to NSPCC helpline
OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FContacts to a helpline regarding
OL,8,Fconcerns for the welfare of young
OL,9,Fpeople in sports clubs rose by almost
OL,10,Fhalf in a year, a children's charity
OL,11,Fhas said.
OL,13,FThe NSPCC Helpline had 623 contacts
OL,14,Ffrom adults across the UK with
OL,15,Fconcerns about a child's welfare in a
OL,16,Fsports setting in the 12 months to the
OL,17,Fend of March.
OL,19,FThis was up from 425 the previous year
OL,20,F` a rise of 47%.
