OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FThe most common concerns raised by
OL,8,Fcontacts to the helpline were about
OL,9,Fsexual abuse or exploitation,
OL,10,Femotional abuse and physical abuse.
OL,12,FChristian McMullan, NSPCC professional
OL,13,Flearning services director, said it is
OL,14,F"vital that parents, carers, staff and
OL,15,Fvolunteers not only know how to spot
OL,16,Fthe signs that a child may be
OL,17,Fexperiencing difficulties, but also
OL,18,Fwhat to do and who to speak to, so
OL,19,Fthat a child can be supported".
